## Requirements to Implement

### 1. Fix MEDIA control to accept PDF/DOCX/ZIP
Current `item_file` MEDIA control has no `media_types` specified, defaults to `['image']`, shows "Escolher imagem" button.  
Fix: Set `'media_types' => ['image', 'application/pdf', 'application/zip', 'application/msword', 'application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document']` on the `item_file` control. Update description text to "PDF, DOCX, ZIP ou imagem. Link criptografado via JetElements."

### 2. Single item = direct download (no dropdown)
When the repeater has exactly 1 valid link, render as a direct `<a>` anchor (not button+dropdown). Same visual appearance, no hover dropdown. The anchor should have the direct download href and `rel="nofollow noopener"`.  
HTML for single mode:
```html
<div class="dropdown-btn-wrapper">
  <div class="dropdown-btn-container">
    <a class="dropdown-btn-toggle dropdown-btn-single" href="..." rel="nofollow noopener">
